Thank you so much for this behind the scenes look, for going through this video step by step for us. It was brutal watching you get beat up, I'm sad that you lived through such pain on your journey.  People can be so cruel...When you started to fight back it was great, when you were on stage in your tuxedo, it was great, but being alone in the station still reflects a back and forth that must be hard to deal with. All Seo in Guks walking forward is brilliant, and there is where the hope lies. You are moving forward any way, in spite of everything, and that is inspiring.  Know that your fans are in your corner, Seo In Guk, always.  So weird since none of us have met, since we do not know all about you, but it is true nonetheless.  We do see enough to love you and your work.  We know enough that we are pulling for you, believe that we believe in you, and no matter what, support you. 

Would be wonderful to see more work from you like this, your instincts and your take as a director are awesome. Will watch all of it, whatever it is. Even the brutal stuff, because I know that you have something to share, and I want to listen, just like with your songs. ğŸŒ¹
